he conventional development tool; developers need to make the changes and then see if any further amendments is required.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This sounds scary. But with Flutter, this issue is resolved. It allows developers to make the changes and see the outcome in real-time. It means the reloading of apps is no more a hassle here. Developers can see in real-time the changes made while the application is running.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Time_to_Market\"><\/span>Time to Market<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For every appreneur one of the biggest challenges is releasing the app faster in the market. Every <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/mobile-app-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mobile App Development company<\/a> addressed <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">this challenge using Flutter. It offers a high-performance and cost-effective app development platform, enabling faster product release in the market.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cons_of_Using_Flutter\"><\/span>Cons of Using Flutter<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11634\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Cons-of-using-Flutter.webp\" alt=\"Disadvantages of flutter\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Cons-of-using-Flutter.webp 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Cons-of-using-Flutter-300x146.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Cons-of-using-Flutter-768x373.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Cons-of-using-Flutter-150x73.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 10