oopener\">React<\/a> offers is that its functionality is not limited to building apps but can be used to develop web and desktop apps.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Due to its cross-platform, cost-effective, and reliable functionalities has become a go-to choice for larger enterprises.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It comes packed with widgets, documentation, libraries, and other tools to give a native-like feel and excellent performance.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><strong><em>Also read- <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/native-web-hybrid-apps-development-one-works.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Native, Web or Hybrid Apps Development? Which One Works for You?<\/a><\/em><\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Top_Brands_Trusting_React_Native\"><\/span>Top Brands Trusting React Native<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bloomberg<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Meta<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UberEats<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Skype<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tesla<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Discord<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shopify<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Instagram<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wallmart<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vo